I don't know if I mentioned that the N.Y.Times mag. asked me for an essay on pornography and that I refused.

Another matter begins to bother me. I am a poor man and if all the LOLITA revenues are lumped together into one income-tax year, there will be very little left for me. I am told that some precautions can be taken when contracts are written. Should I get in touch with a law